the words Milarepa had been desperately waiting for

238
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,666
you're ready for meditation instruction

239
00:09:58,966 --> 00:10:00,833
he handed milarepa a worn scroll

240
00:10:00,833 --> 00:10:02,400
covered in Sanskrit text

