266
00:11:09,966 --> 00:11:12,300
and here's where it gets absolutely wild

267
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:15,200
the transformation was horrifying

268
00:11:15,766 --> 00:11:17,233
his body wasted away

269
00:11:17,233 --> 00:11:20,166
